casebody.data:
BASHA SZYMANSKA v. PLANNING AND ZONING COMMISSION OF THE TOWN OF RIDGEFIELD (AC 22589)

Lavery, C. J., and Bishop and Peters, Js.

Argued February 24 officially released March 18, 2003 Per Curiam.

Due to the approval and recording of a subsequent subdivision application, this appeal from the approval of a prior subdivision application is moot.

The appeal is dismissed.
